Alembic migrations for Callendulla.

Run upgrades:
    alembic upgrade head

Generate a new revision after editing models:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "short summary"

The deploy/entrypoint.sh wrapper runs `alembic upgrade head` once before
starting supervisord, so manual invocation is only needed during dev.

Migration DSN is taken from Settings.db_dsn_sync (default driver psycopg2)
— async drivers don't work in Alembic. To override for ad-hoc runs:
    ALEMBIC_DB_URL=postgresql+psycopg2://... alembic upgrade head
